DataElement.preferredName: Statistics Analysis Plan Document Version Number Text ISO21090.ST.SIMPLE.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: A representation, conceptually a document, that is created to convey the statistical analysis plan version structured content to human beings. A character string that identifies a given collection of content of a document at a point in time. EXAMPLE(S): Could be an integer starting at 1, incrementing by 1, with version number incremented by 1 when a version is replaced, but can also be incremented more often to meet local requirements. NOTE(S): Different versions of same document belong to same document group. Over time, there may be multiple changes to document; allows capture of relationships between changes in instances of document over time; can be new version every time content changes.
